<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥ - <span class="c2">(٢٥٧٧)</span> قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/16352">أَبُو إِسْحَاقَ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا بِهَذَا الْحَدِيثِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/9913">الْحَسَنُ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/17561">وَالْحُسَيْنُ ابْنَا بِشْرٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5983">وَمُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>قَالُوا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3163">أَبُو مُسْهِرٍ </a>فَذَكَرُوا الْحَدِيثَ بِطُولِهِ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>